The '''Skopje Film Festival''' ({{lang-mk|Скопје Филм Фестивал}}) is a film festival held in [[Skopje]], [[Republic of Macedonia]]. The five-day-festival takes part every year in March. Over 50 films are shown at this event, mostly from Macedonia and [[Europe]], but also some non-commercial film productions from all over the world.

