'''Ubombo Ranches Airfield''' {{airport codes||FDUB}} is an airport serving the sugar refinery town<ref>{{cite web |title=Illova Sugar Africa |url=https://www.illovosugarafrica.com/About-us/Swaziland |website=Illova Sugar Swaziland |accessdate=19 June 2018}}</ref> of [[Big Bend, Swaziland|Big Bend]] in [[Lubombo Region]], [[Swaziland]]. The runway is just west of the refinery.
The Ubombo [[non-directional beacon]] (Ident: '''UB''') is on the field.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://skyvector.com/?ll=-26.7821,31.93214&chart=301&zoom=1|title=SkyVector: Flight Planning / Aeronautical Charts|website=skyvector.com|access-date=2018-08-26}}</ref>
